<div class="container-fluid">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="span10 offset1">
      <br />
        <ul style="list-style:none">
          <li>Insert an item: <code>database.insert({"type": "sometype", "aField": "someValue"});
</code></li>
          <li>Look up a single item: <code>return database({"type": "sometype", "anotherField": "someValue"}).first()</code></li>
          <li>Iterate over values: <code>database({"type":"sometype"}).each(function(thedata) {console.log(thedata.type)})</code></li>
          <li>Count items matching a query: <code>database({"type": "sometype", "aField": "someField"}).count()</code></li>
          <li>Order the results: <code>database().order("aField")</code></li>
          <li>Update all matching entries: <code>database().update("aField","value")</code></li>
          <li>Remove the entire database: <code>database().remove()</code></li>
          <li>More at <a href="http://www.taffydb.com/workingwithdata">TaffyDB reference page</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row-fluid">

    <div class="span6">
      <div class="well" style="padding: 9.5px;">
        <div class="query-editor"></div>
        <hr/>
        <button class="run-query btn btn-primary">Run Query</button>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="span6">
      <pre><code class="output json">{{json}}</code></pre>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

